      <h1 class='title'>Departmental Performance Report and Resource Accounts</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 21 November 2002 vol 394 c46WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_46ws' title='Col. 46WS &mdash; HC Deb 21 November 2002 vol 394 c46WS' name='column_46ws' href='#column_46ws' rel='bookmark'>46WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0394P0_20021121_CWS_8'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-geoff-hoon' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0394P0_20021121_CWS_8' title='Link to this speech by Mr Geoff Hoon' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-geoff-hoon" title="Mr Geoff Hoon">The Secretary of State for Defence (Mr. Geoffrey Hoon)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">Information about the Department's performance during the last financial year is contained in<q>the Ministry of Defence Performance Report 2001&#x2013;2002, which will be laid before the House tomorrow as Cm 5661 and</q>
          <q>the Ministry of Defence Consolidated Departmental Resource Accounts 2001&#x2013;02, which will be laid before the House today as HC47.</q>
          Copies of these reports will be placed in the Library of the House. We will also publish them on the Ministry of Defence website.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
